  "label": "Tomas Avenro",
  "description": "This individual is a compact, broad-shouldered human of middle years, marked by a bronze skinTone and the dense forearm musculature associated with repetitive manual work. brown eyes sit beneath heavy brows, giving the face a steady, appraising cast reinforced by a square jaw and blunt cheekbones. brown hair is kept in a short, practical plain style with a slightly receding hairline that emphasizes a high forehead. Fine heat-lines at the temples and old, shallow cuts across the knuckles register a life spent handling glass, metal, and hard counters.",
